# Render the demo GIF.
# Run from the repo root:  vhs scripts/demo.tape
# Output: demo.gif

Output demo.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 720
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 0ms
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font"

Hide
Type "bash scripts/demo.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 22s
